RACE.RACE_TEXT: Mr. Jess Perry S. - Grade3 LOUISIANA DOWNS RACE 6 350 Y Dirt CR: 97. Stakes Purse 25000. FOR ACCREDITED LOUISIANA BRED FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight: 128 lbs. No nomination fee. $250 to pass the entry box and an additional $250 to start. $1,000 Supplemental nomination will be accepted at time of entry and includes all fees. $25,000 Guara nteed of which 60% to the winner, 20% to second, 11% to third, 6% to fourth and 3% to fifth. Starters to be named through the entry box by the usual time of closing. Preference will be given to horses with the highest earnings in 2022 - 2023 at time of en try. Different owners will have equal draw according to earnings. The second part of a same owner entry will have no consideration over a single interest. Failure to draw into the race cancels all fees. Louisiana Downs will present a trophy to the winni ng Owner. Nominations closed Saturday, January 28, 2023 with 24 nominations.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: HEZAA FAST BOY floated out, late surge for score. DIANETOSEPARATEFROMU dueled, led, edged at wire. CWFASTTRACK in mix, outfinished. TF JESS ME altered lane partway. ONE FAST PERRY lost path midway. JJ HEZA FAST DASH JR never fully fired. DENALIA SWEET JESS dancing at break. GO RHONDA GO broke without rider. Following an Inquiry, the board of Stewards determined 5: GO RHONDA GO is declared a NON-STARTER
